== 名言 ==
*''"Here's the 1-1 pitch. It's on the way to Tucker. Drive left-center field in the air coming on quickly Finley he's under it he's got it. And the Padres, drape the National League flag around their shoulders for 1998! Oh ho Doctor!"''（一好一壞，球投向{{lang|en|Tucker}}。球飛向左外野偏中間方向，{{lang|en|Finley}}很快地跑到球的下方，接殺出局。教士把1998年國聯冠軍旗披在身上繞場！喔喔喔！）—教士播報員的{{lang|en|Jerry Coleman}}在最後一個出局後如此播報道。

*''"Driven into deep right field! At the track, at the wall! A three run home run Michael Tucker! And the Atlanta Braves take a 5-4 eighth inning lead!"''（球飛向深遠的右外野！警戒線，全壘打牆！{{lang|en|Michael Tucker}}三分砲！勇士在第八局以5比4領先啦！）—{{lang|en|Joe Buck}}在{{lang|en|Michael Tucker}}第五戰擊出全壘打後如此播報道。

